Usage: set_die_model [-help] [-static_current <string>] [-subckt <string>] {-reset  | [[-die_instance_name <string> [-spice <string> [-mapping <string>]]] ]}

-help                           # Prints out the command usage
-die_instance_name <string>     # <die instance name> (string, optional)
-mapping <string>               # <mapping file> (string, optional)
-reset                          # <reset all previous set_die_model commands>
                                # (bool, optional)
-spice <string>                 # <Spice die model> (string, optional)
-static_current <string>        # <use initial or averge current from pwl
                                # current for static analysis> (string, optional)
-subckt <string>                # <top level sub-circuit name>
                                # (string, optional)